{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1701-06_086","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"À l’heureuse Memoire de Magdeleine de Scudery","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", juin 1701 [tome 8], p. 86-90.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"#":[{"#":{"value":"En vous apprenant le mois dernier la mort de Mademoiselle de Scudery, j’oubliay de vous dire en vous parlant de M","id":"/div/p/#[0]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p/#[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" de Scudery, son Frere, qu’il estoit fameux par beaucoup d’excellens Ouvrages, qui luy avoient fait meriter une place dans l’Academie Françoise, où cette illustre Fille remporta le Prix de l’Eloquence en 1671. Elle avoit dédié ses Conversations de Morale au Roy, qui en 1683. l’avoit gratifiée d’une Pension de deux mille livres. Elle est enterrée dans l’Eglise de Saint Nicolas des Champs. M","id":"/div/p/#[2]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p/#[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" de Vertron a fait son Epitaphe en Latin, pour estre gravée sur son Tombeau. Voicy la version qu’il en a faite en faveur de ceux qui n’entendent pas cette Langue.","id":"/div/p/#[4]/#"}}]},"quote":{"label":{"#1":{"value":"À l’heureuse Memoire","id":"/div/quote/label/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"DE MAGDELEINE DE SCUDERY,","id":"/div/quote/label/#2"}},"lg":{"@rend":"center","l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En pudeur, en fidelité, en esprit,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En pieté, &amp; en grandeur de courage,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Trouvera à peine son égale.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Animée d’une chaste pudeur,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle fleurit, comme le lis parmi","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"les épines.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Excitée par sa fidelité,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce fut un Soleil,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont les rayons &amp; les feux","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"se répandirent sur les Amis.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Soûtenuë par sa pieté,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Semblable à une Aigle,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle s’éleva au dessus de la terre,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour prendre son essor vers le Ciel.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Illustre par son esprit,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle brilla entre nos Muses,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et merita d’estre appellée","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"la sapho de la france.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[18]/hi/#"}}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Munie de la grandeur de son courage,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[19]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle surmonta les foiblesses du corps,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[20]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En invicible Heroïne.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[21]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Triomphant de l’adversité,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[22]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle demeura inébranlable,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[23]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De même qu’un rocher au milieu","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[24]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"des flots.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[25]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les douleurs les plus aiguës","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[26]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne trouvérent en elle qu’une Amazone","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[27]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chrestienne.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[28]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle fut l’honneur de l’un &amp; de l’autre","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[29]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"siecle,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[30]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le precedent la vit naistre,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[31]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Helas ! celui-ci a esté le triste témoin","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[32]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"de sa mort :","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[33]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle ne devoit jamais mourir,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[34]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais il n’y avoit point d’autre chemin","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[35]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"à l’Immortalité.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[36]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cette illustre Fille mourut le","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[37]/hi/#"}},"#":{"value":" 2.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[37]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"du mois de Juin,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[38]/#"}},{"#":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Agée de","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[39]/#[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" 94 ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[39]/#[1]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"ans.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[39]/#[2]/hi/#"}}}]},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’An de Grace M. DCCI.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[40]/#"}}]}}}}